            </div>

            <div class="dissect">
                <div class="dissect-card used">
                    <h4>üîÆ What techniques were used?</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Input first, instruction last</strong> ‚Äî the text
                            block is given, then a precise extraction instruction
                            follows
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Anchor phrase</strong> ("mentioned in the paragraph
                            above") ‚Äî tells the AI to extract from the given text
                            only, not from general knowledge
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Specific target</strong> ("large language model
