                <pre><span class="hl-instruction">Answer the question based on the context below. Keep the answer short and concise. Respond "Unsure about answer" if not sure about the answer.</span>

<span class="hl-context">Context: Teplizumab traces its roots to a New Jersey drug company called Ortho Pharmaceutical. There, scientists generated an early version of the antibody, dubbed OKT3. Originally sourced from mice, the molecule was able to bind to the surface of T cells...</span>

<span class="hl-input">Question: What was OKT3 originally sourced from?</span>

<span class="hl-output-ind">Answer:</span></pre>
            </div>
            <div class="output-wrap">
                <div class="lbl">OUTPUT</div>
                <pre>Mice.</pre>
            </div>

            <div class="dissect">
                <div class="dissect-card used">
                    <h4>üîÆ What techniques were used?</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            All 4 prompt elements: <strong
                                >Instruction + Context + Input + Output
                                Indicator</strong
                            >
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Constraint</strong>: "short and concise" ‚Äî
                            length control
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Fallback instruction</strong>: "Respond
                            'Unsure about answer' if not sure" ‚Äî handles
                            uncertainty safely
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Output Indicator</strong>: "Answer:" ‚Äî
                            anchors where the reply goes
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="dissect-card effect">
                    <h4>‚ö° How did it affect the output?</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            The context grounded the AI ‚Äî it answered from the
                            text, not from training data
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            "Short and concise" ‚Üí one-word answer "Mice." ‚Äî
                            perfectly minimal
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Fallback instruction prevents the AI from guessing
                            or hallucinating when unsure
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="dissect-card violate">
                    <h4>üí• What breaks if you remove it?</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            Remove context ‚Üí AI answers from general knowledge ‚Äî
                            could be wrong or outdated
                        </li>
                        <li>
