        <!-- ===== PAGE 3: TEXT CLASSIFICATION ===== -->
        <div class="page" id="page-3">
            <div class="page-header">
                <h2>üè∑Ô∏è 4. Text Classification</h2>
                <p>
                    The goal: assign a label to a piece of text. This example
