                            example before the real input teaches the exact
                            format
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Output Indicator</strong>: "Sentiment:"
                            anchors the expected response
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Label enumeration</strong>: listing all
                            options ("neutral, negative or positive") scopes the
