                            The example "Sentiment: neutral" taught the AI: use
                            lowercase, return one word only
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Without the example, AI defaulted to its own
                            formatting preference (capitalized)
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            The example overrides the AI's default behavior ‚Äî
                            this is the power of few-shot
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="dissect-card violate">
                    <h4>üí• What breaks if you remove it?</h4>
